WEBVTT

00:00.580 --> 00:02.612
Reporter: Daniel Holden
was released from prison

00:02.614 --> 00:05.316
this week...
How do you feel about that?

00:05.318 --> 00:08.252
Judy Dean: I feel upset.

00:08.254 --> 00:09.855
Sure do.

00:09.857 --> 00:12.725
So, you still believe
Daniel Holden is guilty?

00:12.727 --> 00:14.260
What?

00:14.262 --> 00:16.062
Guilty?

00:16.065 --> 00:20.769
He's as guilty as there's
a hell waitin' on him!

00:20.771 --> 00:26.139
Daniel Holden murdered my baby
girl, and he was convicted to die.

00:26.141 --> 00:29.609
Why ain't he dead, huh?

00:29.611 --> 00:32.043
Why ain't you dead,
Daniel Holden?

00:32.046 --> 00:33.646
Why ain't you dead?

